   SELECT id

    WHERE visibility_level = 0

   UNION ALL

   SELECT id

    WHERE visibility_level = 1
      AND 3 IS NOT NULL

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 3
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 2

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
LEFT JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 3 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 3
      AND (gu.id IS NOT NULL OR FALSE)

   UNION ALL

     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 3 AND gu.owner

 )
) ORDER BY name ASC, "groups"."name" ASC
